        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove screws and end plate (Items 30 and 8,
                <hotlnk xrefid="f0801310">Figure 10</hotlnk>) (if not removed for testing components).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove nut (Item 26) that retains pulley and fan (Item 22). Remove fan and pulley.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove four through bolts (Item 43).</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Separate drive end frame (Item 4) and rotor (Item 2) from rectifier end frame (Item 1) and
                stator (Item 3).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Press rotor (Item 2) from end frame (Item 4).</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove collar (Item 21) from end frame (Item 4).</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove collar (Item 20) from rotor shaft.</para>
        </step1>
